Developer Terms of Use
des:
Soft Sleep Rain Sounds will play 23 high-quality rain soundtracks that will help you sleep better. The rain sounds will help you relax and calm down by hearing the sounds of soft raindrops. 

HOW TO USE:

When you want to get started, say, "Alexa open Soft Sleep Rain-Sounds."

While you are playing the sounds, say "Alexa Next" to play the next sound, or you can say "Alexa Previous" to hear the previous sound.
